Remarks:
Agreed. Heavy rainfall ongoing from last couple of days at Chattogram metro and Chattogram rural area (Potiya, Chandanaish, Anowara, Lohagara, Keranihat & Banshkhali and Bandarban). All area blocked due to worst situation of flood water. No one can moved and no vehicle can not run at that area. All roads under flooded.Whole route is submerged under water. Vehicle can't be moved in the fault location. waterlogging is in very critical condition due to continuous rainfall.
Backbone POP at Bandorban Cantonment POP goes down from  2023-08-07 14:20:00 due to power issue. As per BD Army concern Mr. Arif (01601789399) Commercial Power is unavailable at Cantonment from yesterday. Currently flood water enter into the signal room. For safety reason army concerns dismantle all the active Equipment along with SComm router to the safe place. Our scomm team also try to move towards  Bandorban but due to worst situation of flood water  CTG to Bandonban road is totally Blocked. Bandarban Cantonment POP goes under Water.
After POP renovation by BD Army and  power restored by PG run then team found River crossing OH fiber cut due to storm near PoP over Sangu River. Team pulled 300 meter OH cable over River by arranged boat locally.
Reason: OH Problem : Fiber Cut Due to Storm/Heavy Rain/Flood

Remarks:
Agreed. Heavy rainfall ongoing from last couple of days at Chattogram metro and Chattogram rural area (Potiya, Chandanaish, Anowara, Lohagara, Keranihat & Banshkhali and Bandarban). All area blocked due to worst situation of flood water. No one can moved and no vehicle can not run at that area. All roads under flooded.Whole route is submerged under water. Vehicle can't be moved in the fault location. waterlogging is in very critical condition due to continuous rainfall.
Backbone POP at Bandorban Cantonment POP goes down from  2023-08-07 14:20:00 due to power issue. As per BD Army concern Mr. Arif (01601789399) Commercial Power is unavailable at Cantonment from yesterday. Currently flood water enter into the signal room. For safety reason army concerns dismantle all the active Equipment along with SComm router to the safe place. Our scomm team also try to move towards  Bandorban but due to worst situation of flood water  CTG to Bandonban road is totally Blocked. Bandarban Cantonment POP goes under Water.
After POP renovation by BD Army and  power restored by PG run then team found River crossing OH fiber cut due to storm near PoP over Sangu River. Team pulled 300 meter OH cable over River by arranged boat locally.  
Landslide and raod collapsed at Bandarban sadar to Thanci road. road damaged & land slide issue in several portions from  Bandarban sadar to Thanchi  and   Alikodam to Thanci road.
Also our team tried to move but fail due to road collapse issue. Team tried to move there all alternative way but can not possible cause of no local transport there.   Thanci is totally isolated from Bandarban. No other option to bypass the connectivity. Road authority is working there and  after completing their task team can move this side.
Escalation delayed. Escalated to RIO end after 1:13:00 Hr
Reason: OH Problem : Fiber Cut by Cable TV/ISP/Local Authority
